nodes.text: Grayeg Wintozzen was the Human male Moff of a star system near Naboo. He visited the Emperor's Retreat around 1 ABY and was nearly the victim of an attempted assassination by a Rebel cadre. Fortunately, a loyal Imperial found the Governor, and escorted him back to the safe confines of the Emperor's Retreat.

Wintozzen appeared in the "Imperial Theme Park" series of quests in Star Wars Galaxies prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. After September 14, 2007, the quests in which Wintozzen appears were replaced with a different set.
